subSubSection.paragraph:
Movements, Home range and Social organization.
Ben Keith’s Short-tailed Bat seems to have small home ranges. It will share hollow trees with congeners such as the Silky Short-tailed Bat (C. brevicaudum), Seba’s Short-tailed Bat (
C. perspicillata
), and the Proboscis Bat (
Rhynchonycteris naso
).
